267
00:23:04,290 --> 00:23:07,640
She has needed a lot of sleeping pills to sleep.

268
00:23:24,950 --> 00:23:27,660
[Green Mountain Psychiatric Sanatorium]

269
00:23:34,870 --> 00:23:37,080
Is this a scent that Mr. He is familiar with?

270
00:23:37,080 --> 00:23:39,230
Yes. This is the scent of cedar.

271
00:23:39,230 --> 00:23:41,130
It has a special meaning to Tianxing.

272
00:23:41,130 --> 00:23:44,300
That’s very good. Meaningful scents and sounds

273
00:23:44,300 --> 00:23:47,360
