274
00:23:52,770 --> 00:23:54,290
What’s wrong?

275
00:23:54,290 --> 00:23:56,720
His willpower is very strong,

276
00:23:56,720 --> 00:24:01,530
but his physical condition is rapidly deteriorating.

277
00:24:01,530 --> 00:24:04,290
Now, he’s starting to exhibit signs of organ failure.

278
00:24:04,290 --> 00:24:06,190
Is it because we moved him last time?

279
00:24:06,190 --> 00:24:08,480
That shouldn’t be the reason.

280
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:11,270
So far, we haven’t found the reason.

281
00:24:11,270 --> 00:24:13,730
Besides changing his location,

282
00:24:13,730 --> 00:24:16,110
other external conditions have not changed.

283
00:24:16,110 --> 00:24:17,630
Then what should we do?

284
00:24:17,630 --> 00:24:19,530
I will do my best.

285
00:24:26,980 --> 00:24:28,630
How did this happen?

286
00:24:28,630 --> 00:24:32,170
Tianxing, something happened to He Mingli.

287
00:24:32,170 --> 00:24:35,090
Tianliang Group will definitely undergo reoganization in the future.

288
00:24:35,090 --> 00:24:38,670
You better quickly wake up to save Tianliang and yourself.

289
00:24:38,670 --> 00:24:41,520
Even He Mingli was reduced to this state.

290
00:24:41,520 --> 00:24:43,470
I’m afraid that they won’t let you off

291
00:24:43,470 --> 00:24:45,410
and insist on killing you.

292
00:24:45,410 --> 00:24:47,110
All right, all right. Everything’s fine now.

293
00:24:47,110 --> 00:24:49,260
Let’s stop scaring ourselves.

294
00:24:49,260 --> 00:24:51,860
