The magnolia lady knocked on my car window to sold them.

324
00:27:10,100 --> 00:27:12,770
That won’t do. It’s too silly.

325
00:27:21,280 --> 00:27:23,400
Don’t be too touched.

326
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:27,130
You're so touched, right?

327
00:27:27,130 --> 00:27:31,380
Take it. These are the flowers I got for you.

328
00:27:36,390 --> 00:27:41,840
Zheng Xiao’en, I specially bought flowers for you. Where are you?

329
00:27:41,840 --> 00:27:43,080
I went home.

330
00:27:43,080 --> 00:27:45,080
Why did you go home?

331
00:27:45,080 --> 00:27:47,130
I hadn't showered or changed my clothes.

332
00:27:47,130 --> 00:27:49,000
If I didn't go home, what else would I do?

333
00:27:49,870 --> 00:27:51,590
You wait there.

334
00:27:57,320 --> 00:27:59,080
What?

335
00:28:00,570 --> 00:28:06,590
