336
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:10,520
Aiyo, I’m not that charming.

337
00:28:10,520 --> 00:28:12,260
We just haven't seen each other for a day,

338
00:28:12,260 --> 00:28:15,840
but he’s acting like we haven’t met for three autumns.

339
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:22,520
Give me the main lead's ring of light!

340
00:28:24,850 --> 00:28:27,970
Why am I wearing one sock with leopard print and another with zebra print?

341
00:28:32,500 --> 00:28:36,520
Oh my god, how can I meet people in this state?

342
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:45,230
Where’s that foot mask that Qiutian gave me last time

343
00:28:45,230 --> 00:28:48,520
