00:42:43,130 --> 00:42:49,980
Zheng Xiao'en, you're the most special one in the world.

467
00:42:56,840 --> 00:42:58,610
Aoran.

468
00:43:20,300 --> 00:43:21,980
Wait for me.

469
00:43:47,380 --> 00:43:51,670
Let's go. Let me show you an upgraded version.

470
00:44:06,740 --> 00:44:08,810
The remote isn't here?

471
00:44:09,870 --> 00:44:11,350
What day and age is it?

472
00:44:11,350 --> 00:44:13,440
Who uses a remote anymore?

473
00:44:16,360 --> 00:44:19,590
What do you want to watch? Tell me.

474
00:44:24,100 --> 00:44:26,970
Continuously laying down here is tiring.

475
00:44:28,010 --> 00:44:31,250
Reach out your arm in the four o'clock direction.

476
00:44:34,600 --> 00:44:36,890
Wow.

477
00:45:09,250 --> 00:45:11,810
[One more piece]

478
00:45:26,100 --> 00:45:28,080
What is this?

479
00:45:29,830 --> 00:45:32,290
[One more love kiss]

480
00:45:36,460 --> 00:45:39,570
This is what you call innovation.

481
00:45:55,200 --> 00:45:57,300
What are you doing?

482
00:46:11,100 --> 00:46:13,060
I want to drink something.

483
00:46:14,750 --> 00:46:16,730
The cup is on your side.

484
00:46:35,640 --> 00:46:40,000
What do you think? Is this place scrappy enough?

485
00:46:42,340 --> 00:46:45,650
It's not bad, but it's missing a commoner's vibe.

486
00:46:46,650 --> 00:46:48,520
I tried my best.

487
00:46:48,970 --> 00:46:50,990
I know.

488
00:46:54,840 --> 00:46:59,040
My place here definitely has something special that your place doesn't have.

489
00:46:59,670 --> 00:47:01,500
What?

490
00:47:01,500 --> 00:47:05,710
If you don't like that the bathroom is far away, I can carry you there.

491
00:47:05,710 --> 00:47:08,910
You just have to give me a kiss.

492
00:47:10,120 --> 00:47:12,520
Go away.

493
00:47:14,910 --> 00:47:18,130
Are you free after work tomorrow?

494
00:47:18,150 --> 00:47:22,160
What? If you treat me to lobster, I'll go.

495
00:47:22,160 --> 00:47:23,780
It can be as expensive as you want it to be.

496
00:47:23,780 --> 00:47:25,940
You can't eat till you bankrupt me.

497
00:47:27,120 --> 00:47:31,450
Okay. I'm not afraid.

498
00:47:31,450 --> 00:47:34,180
Give me a kiss and there'll be one more ounce of lobster.

499
00:47:34,180 --> 00:47:35,690
What's there to be afraid of?

500
00:47:35,690 --> 00:47:38,940
You better prepare 100 ounces of lobster.

501
00:47:38,940 --> 00:47:42,210
- Hey, I said to kiss—
