502
00:47:42,890 --> 00:47:48,100
1 ounce, 2 ounces, 3 ounces, 4 ounces, 5 ounces, 6 ounces.

503
00:47:48,100 --> 00:47:50,630
7, 8, 9, 10.

504
00:47:50,630 --> 00:47:53,530
100 ounces of lobster!

