513
00:48:29,140 --> 00:48:33,240
I just wanted to fight for it. Is that also wrong?

514
00:48:33,240 --> 00:48:35,620
Zheng Xiao'en can fight for it.

515
00:48:35,620 --> 00:48:37,010
Why can't I?

516
00:48:37,010 --> 00:48:39,800
Xiao'en at least had a bottom line.

517
00:48:39,800 --> 00:48:42,310
She never hurt you.

518
00:48:45,400 --> 00:48:47,970
Let's go. I'll take you home.

519
00:48:49,810 --> 00:48:51,740
