01:09:39,430 --> 01:09:46,090
♫ Sleepwalking the whole world together ♫

775
01:09:46,090 --> 01:09:51,270
♫ How warm the sun is ♫

776
01:09:53,520 --> 01:09:56,340
♫ Feel it to your heart's content ♫

777
01:09:56,340 --> 01:10:00,240
♫ Got nothing but time ♫

778
01:10:00,240 --> 01:10:07,230
♫ I will accompany you in insomnia ♫

779
01:10:07,230 --> 01:10:11,310
♫ You don't need to face everything alone ♫

780
01:10:11,310 --> 01:10:14,320
You have that much to talk about with Qingfeng?

781
01:10:14,320 --> 01:10:15,640
♫ No matter how hard the pain is, forever ♫

782
01:10:15,640 --> 01:10:18,930
Zheng Xiao'en, I have faith in you.

783
01:10:18,930 --> 01:10:22,460
Please don't disappoint me.

784
01:10:22,460 --> 01:10:23,860
Are you planning to propose to me?

785
01:10:23,860 --> 01:10:28,000
If you knew that we would disappear after having the wedding,

786
01:10:28,000 --> 01:10:29,980
would you still marry me?

787
01:10:29,980 --> 01:10:32,820
Didn't you propose to Zheng Xiao'en?

788
01:10:32,820 --> 01:10:35,840
Xiao'en, come wander with me in a different story.

789
01:10:35,840 --> 01:10:37,600
That way you won't disappear.

790
01:10:37,600 --> 01:10:40,670
This disappearance you speak of... Where is it disappearing to?

791
01:10:40,670 --> 01:10:45,270
Qingfeng, is there something you know about Xiao'en?

792
01:10:45,270 --> 01:10:49,200
Being able to participate in your past just now is already very wonderful.

793
01:10:49,200 --> 01:10:50,920
I have a wish.

794
01:10:50,920 --> 01:10:52,820
Can you help me fulfill it?

795
01:10:52,820 --> 01:10:56,610
Can you not forget me?

796
01:11:07,980 --> 01:11:11,330
♫ Memories wear protective coloration ♫

797
01:11:11,330 --> 01:11:14,390
♫ Ambushing in the middle of the night ♫

798
01:11:14,390 --> 01:11:19,900
♫ A quiet strike ♫

799
01:11:19,900 --> 01:11:23,110
♫ Streetlights awaiting dusk ♫

800
01:11:23,110 --> 01:11:25,400
♫ Still awaiting as always ♫

801
01:11:25,400 --> 01:11:28,510
♫ Nothing is impossible ♫

802
01:11:28,510 --> 01:11:32,890
♫ Even if no one is perfect ♫

803
01:11:32,890 --> 01:11:37,540
♫ Holding you next to my heartbeat ♫

804
01:11:37,540 --> 01:11:40,680
♫ Tightly held the palm of my hand ♫

805
01:11:40,680 --> 01:11:45,760
♫ It remains the only farewell ♫

806
01:11:45,760 --> 01:11:50,450
♫ If I could see you again ♫

807
01:11:50,450 --> 01:11:57,120
♫ Carefully planning my gamble with you ♫

808
01:11:57,120 --> 01:12:01,230
♫ In the end I lost to you ♫

809
01:12:01,230 --> 01:12:10,440
♫ I think of you until I can no longer breathe ♫

810
01:12:10,440 --> 01:12:14,240
♫ If you were a painter ♫

811
01:12:14,240 --> 01:12:16,180
♫ Then I'll be your canvas ♫

812
01:12:16,180 --> 01:12:20,470
♫ No regrets ♫

813
01:12:20,470 --> 01:12:26,930
♫ I lost all my love to you ♫
